{"tid":2342490,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（拋磚引玉）連登可唔可以搞返個《2020全年之星選舉》？","createTime":"2020-12-27T07:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T09:39:19.000Z","uid":14436,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0f468f2d4d5ff2797b5f4771396a5956f2ea457f","tid":2342490,"uid":14436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:28:44.000Z","msg":"見到2020年發生咁多事，就諗返起以前高登有個每月之星/全年之星選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係咁想拋磚引玉，睇下可唔可以搞個《全連做星2020》<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到<br />\n<br />\n<ins>現實組提名：</ins><br />\n- 李偲嫣<br />\n- 陳肇始<br />\n- Popo<br />\n- 柒婆<br />\n- 屎家軍<br />\n⋯etc<br />\n<br />\n<ins>連登會員組提名</ins><br />\n- 木耳<br />\n- 媽咪麵<br />\n- 有落呀屌你老母 <br />\n⋯etc<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>特別提名全球之星</ins><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">武漢肺炎病毒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其他交俾各位巴打絲打發功<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b933a635c748056586202fe8e824a21635101dcf","tid":2342490,"uid":14436,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e45f37ef317766c206fd561eb4c0d357b2add5","tid":2342490,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:48:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1da9f2be8a153756f9b02dd761225427c3433f9","tid":2342490,"uid":14436,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c7e45f37ef317766c206fd561eb4c0d357b2add5","tid":2342490,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:48:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:55:56.000Z","msg":"年尾發功<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cut.gif\" class=\"